In sailing mode:


The mouse is locked by default, and you can use the <color="#FD965ECC">[TAB]</color> key to switch the mouse lock;
Hold down the [Forward key] to make the mecha's sailing direction turn to the front of the camera;
<color="#FD965ECC">Hold down the [SHIFT] key to accelerate, [Backward key] to slow down;</color>
Use [Q][R] keys to sideward flight, hold down [Right mouse button] drag to roll the camera sideways.


In sailing mode, you can control the mecha travel to different planets or planetary systems by following the arrows in the Space Navigation.

